{"tid":477081,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[放負]偶爾會記起已成過客嘅前好朋友","createTime":"2017-11-22T15:51:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T17:40:48.000Z","uid":74988,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6b4189cce0555a087420a56170e8d1004d071cb0","tid":477081,"uid":74988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:51:49.000Z","msg":"你哋過得還好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想話俾你哋聽我間唔中仲會諗起你哋每一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好掛住同你哋一齊嘅時光<br />\n點解我哋會成為彼此過客<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解同你哋一齊開心唔開心嘅時光只能夠回憶而唔可以重演<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aea815c976148e3c3ebb0c3e7a5a1e437396d7d","tid":477081,"uid":63360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:53:27.000Z","msg":"Hi"},{"pid":"cf611356b5e9fe35b054b9a3821530a9e604ab68","tid":477081,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:54:58.000Z","msg":"樓主冇諗過揾返人地？"},{"pid":"9c0207beaf0227d08d0c3f203b98247767e2eb9f","tid":477081,"uid":74988,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T17:31:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主冇諗過揾返人地？</blockquote><br />\n喺我錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一時意氣做錯野/講錯野趕走咗你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果可以俾你哋打我一鑊跟住你哋會返嚟嘅話，唔該打到我入醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果有如果"},{"pid":"e51a0a8cfd7308c0e9a4d584fca00b914a294849","tid":477081,"uid":5921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T20:06:14.000Z","msg":"我成日都手痕搵返人 可能講幾句咁<br />\n過多幾個月又搵 一直loop<br />\n心入面諗可能搵搵吓突然會frd返都唔定<br />\n<br />\n個啲所謂既刺 傷痕<br />\n我發現我幾個月就會忘記<br />\n然後無壓力咁搵返人<br />\n但我諗人地對住我有壓力<br />\n如果個個都好似我咁就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5058d65cc6c6806421a61b0726a2b4aa55cc032b","tid":477081,"uid":17148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T20:23:25.000Z","msg":"有時都會諗起以前一位好朋友<br />\n其實都唔知點解斷左contact<br />\n可能係我自卑<br />\n佢就傳統名校高材生<br />\n我就地區雞校排第尾咁制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n漸漸就沒聯絡 <br />\n事隔差唔多十年<br />\n而家係同一間學校讀<br />\n但我已經都唔敢搵返佢"},{"pid":"e5c0ff87207f9fcc73e0f305ee0846d90014b252","tid":477081,"uid":74988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T01:22:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時都會諗起以前一位好朋友<br />\n其實都唔知點解斷左contact<br />\n可能係我自卑<br />\n佢就傳統名校高材生<br />\n我就地區雞校排第尾咁制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n漸漸就沒聯絡 <br />\n事隔差唔多十年<br />\n而家係同一間學校讀<br />\n但我已經都唔敢搵返佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abc126c6b99bac5981a9f1add8b8540dc2883b39","tid":477081,"uid":22505,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T01:32:49.000Z","msg":"我同e個朋友識左半年<br />\n兩個月前佢開始變淡<br />\n以前成日日傾夜傾<br />\ne加變到已經4日冇whatsapp我了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔明點解之前成日大家都會講心事<br />\n又會知道大家既過去<br />\n佢話想去邊我就陪佢去<br />\n佢唔開心我就即坐半個鍾車程出黎陪佢飲酒<br />\n總知佢想出街我就隨時隨到咁<br />\n以前成日可以揾大家日傾夜傾<br />\ne加居然可以變到格幾日先傾一次<br />\n仲要e加變到我主動約佢佢都唔肯出黎<br />\n明明知己兩隻字係你自己講<br />\n我仲以為知己可以做一世<br />\n我仲以為雙方認定左<br />\n大家係知己友誼可以好長久<br />\n但原來唔係<br />\n果然期望越大失望就越大<br />\n每日比e個人搞到好唔開心<br />\n每次得返自己一個人既時候<br />\n靜落黎既時候一諗起佢我就忍唔住喊<br />\n我真係好唔甘心"},{"pid":"fe3ac6d37c4dfe24d060b1381b6267ccbd19fb5b","tid":477081,"uid":74988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T05:47:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我同e個朋友識左半年<br />\n兩個月前佢開始變淡<br />\n以前成日日傾夜傾<br />\ne加變到已經4日冇whatsapp我了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔明點解之前成日大家都會講心事<br />\n又會知道大家既過去<br />\n佢話想去邊我就陪佢去<br />\n佢唔開心我就即坐半個鍾車程出黎陪佢飲酒<br />\n總知佢想出街我就隨時隨到咁<br />\n以前成日可以揾大家日傾夜傾<br />\ne加居然可以變到格幾日先傾一次<br />\n仲要e加變到我主動約佢佢都唔肯出黎<br />\n明明知己兩隻字係你自己講<br />\n我仲以為知己可以做一世<br />\n我仲以為雙方認定左<br />\n大家係知己友誼可以好長久<br />\n但原來唔係<br />\n果然期望越大失望就越大<br />\n每日比e個人搞到好唔開心<br />\n每次得返自己一個人既時候<br />\n靜落黎既時候一諗起佢我就忍唔住喊<br />\n我真係好唔甘心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為大家生活環境同圈子唔同咗？"},{"pid":"950e8edfad1933ea590fa6b1dc8a3a842a5b0ea9","tid":477081,"uid":40509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T06:07:15.000Z","msg":"見到面都無打招乎既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能呢個係我同佢最後既默契"},{"pid":"9c96cdb2db033fd5135a746d4ac853e83788de45","tid":477081,"uid":74988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T15:16:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到面都無打招乎既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能呢個係我同佢最後既默契</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁樣嘅默契我唔想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2613e5e680cf73b93cabaf8263eca2b20a426e79","tid":477081,"uid":79278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T14:29:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主冇諗過揾返人地？</blockquote><br />\n喺我錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fac